text: Jean-Pierre Le Lain (born 23 September 1961) is a French rower. He competed in the men's coxless four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:French male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of France Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
